Titolo: Armour-Geddon

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Armour-Geddon is a 3D video game developed and published in 1991 by Psygnosis for the Amiga, MS-DOS and Atari ST.
In 1994, a sequel was released, titled Armour-Geddon 2: Codename Hellfire. Unlike the original Armour-Geddon, it was only released for Amiga, and it was only released in Europe.